{"componentChunkName":"component---src-page-post-tsx","path":"/codefreeze-brings-the-magic-of-socrates-to-lapland","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Markus Tacker","tagLine":"Software Crafter","description":"Software Crafter building üå©Ô∏è cloud-based cellular IoT solutions at Nordic Semiconductor.‚Äã\n\t\tMentor. Speaker. ‚ÄãConference & Community builder. Camper. üèïÔ∏è üöê","gitHubUrl":"https://github.com/coderbyheart/coderbyheart.com.git","siteUrl":"https://coderbyheart.com","twitter":"@coderbyheart","defaultCard":"https://images.ctfassets.net/bncv3c2gt878/3Jk4P6nFPNzaz1gsguktk8/350b7e4ddb2c7d86416243d9902920e2/social-card-default-2020.png"}}},"pageContext":{"page":{"id":"183577d4-e366-507e-9193-966978035cbb","name":"codefreeze-brings-the-magic-of-socrates-to-lapland","relativeDirectory":"post","relativePath":"post/codefreeze-brings-the-magic-of-socrates-to-lapland.md","remark":{"htmlAst":{"children":[{"children":[{"properties":{"src":"//images.ctfassets.net/bncv3c2gt878/223gM2KwD5AMjAHqhh024J/a11044bad774d40f034569437ab81134/2017-01-21-codefreeze-brings-the-magic-of-socrates-to-lapland.jpg?w=4084&h=2718","alt":"Kiilop√§√§, Finland"},"children":[],"tagName":"img","type":"element"}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"For the last week we have been in "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Kiilop√§√§"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"http://www.kiilopaa.fi/en/home.html","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":", a national park in the\narctic circle to attend "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"codefreeze"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"http://codefreeze.fi","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" which brings the "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Software Craft and\nTesting Conferences"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://socrates-conference.de/","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" to one of the most remote places I have ever\nvisited. I was drawn there by the "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"pictures I saw on Twitter"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://twitter.com/search?f=tweets&vertical=default&q=%23codefreeze&src=typd","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" of last\nyear and this year, I could contribute a fair share of my own."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"The conference has been a breathtaking experience and we will definitely be go\nthere again, not only for the conference, but for the beautiful nature that the\nnational park offers. And with a direct flight from Frankfurt to Ivalo, which is\njust a 40 minute bus drive from Kiilop√§√§ it is easy to go there for us. We even\nhad Finns, that had longer journeys to reach this remote spot in the arctic\ncircle where there is basically nothing for hundreds of kilometers."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"The national park itself is around 40 kilometers in diameter and preservers a\nnatural fern forest with very old trees, they can reach up to 300 years before\nthey die and will then keep standing for another 50 or more years."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Soumen Latu"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.suomenlatu.fi/","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" is a charitable organization in Finland that aims to preserve\nthe nature which operates the Fjell Center where we stayed. It's a small village\nwith a main building where you will get great food basically all day, which has\na rental shop and a public sauna that is on all day. Next to it is a hostel for\ngroups and a hotel with rooms for one to two persons. We stayed in one of the\nroughly 40 cabins that house two to ten people. Our log cabin of 50 m¬≤ was\nequipped with it's own sauna and a fireplace."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#absolute-silence","ariaLabel":"absolute silence permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Absolute Silence"}],"tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"absolute-silence","style":"position:relative;"},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"With the next supermarket being 26 km away and the airport around 40 km, no\nindustry a ban for snowmobiles in the area the nights were absolutely silent.\nAnd even at day, when being just a few hundred meters away from the main\nbuilding, you would hear "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"not a thing"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"The masses of snow, that blanketed the area created an incredible atmosphere and\na fascinating black and white backdrop for the many outdoor activities you could\nhave: between 1000 and 1500 the sun was above the horizon‚Äînot visible from the\nfjell center, though‚Äîand here we did nordic skiing, snowshoe trips and\nbackcountry ski trips guided by the volunteers of the Soumen Latu association\nthat come to Kiilop√§√§ to stay there for two or more weeks receiving free\naccommodation for their services. The trips were free of charge, you only had to\nrent the necessary equipment in the rental shop at the main building for a\nreasonable price‚Äîe.g a pair of snowshoes and poles for 10 ‚Ç¨ per day."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#perfect-winter-vacation-snow-and-sauna","ariaLabel":"perfect winter vacation snow and sauna permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Perfect winter vacation: snow and sauna"}],"tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"perfect-winter-vacation-snow-and-sauna","style":"position:relative;"},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"The trips would take you to the area around which offers a lot of variety: dense\nforests with deep snow, prepared tracks for nordic skiing or you could go above\nthe treeline on top of the Kiilop√§√§‚Äîthe 600m high mountain that the center is\nnamed after. Usually you would start in the morning around 10‚Äîthat's when\nbreakfast ends‚Äîand be home in the early afternoon‚Äîit got dark around 1500‚Äîto\ntake a nap and then go to the sauna. And even with sauna there is variety: you\nhave the "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"normal"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" finnish sauna in the cabin with an electric oven, it heats up\nquickly to 100¬∞ and you can set it up in advance, to time it perfectly for your\nreturn. But there is also smoke sauna, a big sauna for roughly 30 people that is\nwarmed at noon with a open wooden fire which heats up a big pile of stones that\nkeep the warmth for hours. The smoke sauna can then be used between 1500 and\n2000 and has a totally different heat which is less intense and you can stay\nthere for three hours‚Äîonce in a while you will go out and take "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"the dip"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":", a\nsmall pond that is kept ice-free by a flowing water source and has a temperature\nof around 1¬∞. It sounds scary at first, but it's actually a great feeling,\nespecially when your feet start to freeze to the ground after leaving the water\n‚Ä¶"}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#the-codefreeze-unconference","ariaLabel":"the codefreeze unconference permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"The codefreeze unconference"}],"tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"the-codefreeze-unconference","style":"position:relative;"},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"To be honest, we never planned to make this trip about the conference, it was a\ngreat occasion to be there but it was clear that this would be more of a leisure\ntrip, which is why I didn't make this trip on the company budget. But we had\nthree and a half days, starting on Monday afternoon where we had a "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"proper"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\nunconference, you can see for yourself "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"on the trello board for the\nweek"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://trello.com/b/zIYeI0me/codefreeze-2017","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":", given the small group‚Äîaround 20 attendees‚Äîwe still managed to\nfill the timetable with a great variety of topics. But a lot of discussion\nhappened outside of the sessions and that's what made it especially great to be\nhere. Although you had so many outdoor activities, everybody would always return\nto the main building for food, or the sauna, or some of the cabins where the\ndiscussions continued or new topics arised."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"For me it was the best conference experience I could imagine and it was also the\nbest winter vacation I ever had. We will definitely return to Kiilop√§√§ and not\nonly during codefreeze season but also in the summer, to hike in the woods there\nfrom hut to hut. I'm very grateful for "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Aki"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/rinkkasatiainen/de","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" adding this experience to my\nlife. I will never forget my first codefreeze."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"}],"type":"root","data":{"quirksMode":false}},"frontmatter":{"title":"codefreeze brings the magic of SoCraTes to Lapland","subtitle":"A conference about Software Craft like no other","noheadline":null,"date":"2017-01-21T10:00+02:00","abstract":"About codefreeze, the software craft and testing conference in the arctic circle","lang":null},"headings":[{"id":"absolute-silence","depth":2,"value":"Absolute Silence"},{"id":"perfect-winter-vacation-snow-and-sauna","depth":2,"value":"Perfect winter vacation: snow and sauna"},{"id":"the-codefreeze-unconference","depth":2,"value":"The codefreeze unconference"}]}},"Footer":{"id":"cfe5b9e2-511c-5615-992a-dab82e1f8ed7","name":"Footer","relativeDirectory":"","relativePath":"Footer.md","remark":{"htmlAst":{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Software Crafter building üå©Ô∏è cloud-based cellular IoT solutions at\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Nordic Semiconductor"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://nordicsemi.com/","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"."